text: Casie Lauren Bowry (born 10 April 1991) is a female former water polo player from New Zealand. She was part of the New Zealand team at the 2009, 2011, 2013 and 2017 Fina World Aquatics Championships 2007 and 2009 Junior World Aquatics Championships, 2016/Olympic Qualifiers, Gouda. == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
